{
  "text": "We note here we have assumed an adiabatic SPIO response, whereby the particle response is instantaneous to the applied field and has been shown to be accurate for many formulations of SPIOs and MPI scanning parameters [CITATION_1] , [CITATION_2] . However, as magnetic relaxation effects increase for varying SPIO particles (of larger core diameters, for example), MPI image resolution and (SNR) can suffer significantly [CITATION_3] .",
  "correct_citation": {
